
    <html xmlns:o="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" 
          xmlns:w="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:word" 
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40">
    <head>
        <title>Requirement Analysis - Technology Stack & Architecture</title>
        <style>
            body {
                font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', Arial, sans-serif;
                line-height: 1.6;
                color: #2d2724;
                background-color: #faf6eb;
                margin: 20px;
            }
            h1 {
                font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;
                color: #c05c46;
                border-bottom: 2px solid #2d2724;
                padding-bottom: 5px;
            }
            h2, h3, h4 {
                font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;
                color: #2d2724;
            }
            table {
                width: 100%;
                border-collapse: collapse;
                margin: 20px 0;
            }
            th, td {
                border: 2px solid #2d2724;
                padding: 10px;
                text-align: left;
            }
            th {
                background-color: #dda15e;
                color: #2d2724;
                font-weight: bold;
            }
            .meta-table {
                width: 50%;
                margin-bottom: 30px;
            }
            .meta-table th {
                background-color: #2d2724;
                color: #faf6eb;
            }
            .highlight {
                background-color: #faf6eb;
                font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;
                padding: 2px 5px;
                border: 1px solid #2d2724;
            }
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>
        <h1>Requirement Analysis - Technology Stack & Architecture</h1>
        <table class="meta-table">
            <tr><th>Parameter</th><th>Value</th></tr>
            <tr><td><b>Date</b></td><td>11 July 2026</td></tr>
            <tr><td><b>Team ID</b></td><td>TEAM-MERN-03</td></tr>
            <tr><td><b>Project Name</b></td><td>ShopEZ - Vintage Sepia Neubrutalist E-Commerce Platform</td></tr>
        </table>
        
    <h2>Technical Stack Components</h2>
    <table>
        <tr><th>S.No</th><th>Component</th><th>Description</th><th>Technology Stack</th></tr>
        <tr>
            <td>1</td>
            <td>User Interface</td>
            <td>Retro Neubrutalist Web View</td>
            <td>HTML5, Vanilla CSS3 (Courier Prime & Space Mono Google Fonts), React.js, React Router</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>2</td>
            <td>Application Logic</td>
            <td>REST APIs for auth, order processing, and catalogs</td>
            <td>Node.js, Express.js (Modular Route/Controller pattern)</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>3</td>
            <td>Schema Validations</td>
            <td>Input sanitization middleware layers</td>
            <td>Joi schema structures</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>4</td>
            <td>Database</td>
            <td>Document store for users, orders, and items</td>
            <td>MongoDB, Mongoose ORM</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>5</td>
            <td>Session Security</td>
            <td>Token encryption and auth validation guards</td>
            <td>JSON Web Tokens (JWT), Bcrypt</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>6</td>
            <td>Payment Mock Gateway</td>
            <td>Simulated credit card processor</td>
            <td>React stateful 3D Flip, asynchronous timeout loops</td>
        </tr>
    </table>

    <h2>Application Architecture Security</h2>
    <p><b>JWT Access Verification:</b> Users authenticate via logins, generating secure JWTs placed in the <span class="highlight">Authorization: Bearer</span> headers of subsequent API requests.</p>
    <p><b>Stale Token Interceptor:</b> Active Axios response interceptor monitors for 401 response codes. If a stale token is found, it clears the token and returns the client to the login screen.</p>
    
    </body>
